247
00:22:53.149 --> 00:22:56.328
- Paul!
- Hej, fader.


248
00:22:56.527 --> 00:23:01.616
Jag ville gratulera dig.
Bravo. Det var goda nyheter!


249
00:23:01.824 --> 00:23:04.125
Tack så mycket.

250
00:23:04.326 --> 00:23:10.876
